Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
hello, I would like to schedule a viewing at North Hill apartments
What is your name?
Could you give me your name, please?
Angela
You suddenly remember that you have a friend's wedding on Monday at 6 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
what day?
What day would you like to make the booking for?
Monday at 6 pm
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
application fee paid?
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
Can we change the date to Tuesday. I forgot I have a wedding to attend.

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
application fee
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
I am not sure.
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your friend's wedding. [instruction 5 of 6]
it is available on tuesday.
I am showing it as available on the Tuesday, should I book?
Yes please.
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
